{"lastModified":1760022635504,"uri":"c::18277099312::vessel::e251b4c0-f066-11ee-b775-039fbd1e3d2d","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Operating Area: Croatia\n\nLagoon 51 - Negroni, is an elegant catamaran that accommodates up to 8 guests in 4 double cabins with en-suite bathrooms, 2 adult guests or 4 children in smaller inner cabins without bathrooms. There are also a crew cabin and a crew head in the bow. In case you would like to hire a hostess or a chef, one of the inner cabins should be appointed to him/her.\n\nThe design of the Lagoon 51 perfectly integrates indoor with outdoor living spaces. The spacious saloon, attractive flybridge and large aft and forward cockpit make this yacht the perfect destination for relaxation. Keep company to our professional skipper during navigation or just have fun with your friends or family on the modular seating on the flybridge. Large transoms allow safe and easy access to the dock side and/or the water and water toys. And the forward cockpit has an unobstructed sea view.\n\nLagoon 51 - Negroni is excellently equipped with generator, inverter, air-conditioning and heating, watermaker, icemaker, TV with DVD, Fusion Appollo audio system with cockpit speakers, and Wi-Fi. Enjoy the protection of the flybridge and cockpit sun covers, and the comfort of cushions and cockpit shower. Moreover, the hydraulic platform for the tender with 20 hp outboard engine makes launching of the dinghy a child's play, and becomes your own private beach on board. The complete galley equipment consists of a freezer, coffee maker, dishwasher, micorwave and stove with oven.\n\nHave fun with a water tube, electric scooter, S.U.P. board, snorkel equipment, seascooter and Jobe Infinity Comfort Chair. Charter Lagoon 51 with our friendly and professional skipper and get cozy and recharge your batteries sailing along Dalmatian coast abord Negroni.","blueprint":{"name":"NEGRONI","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::e251b4c0-f066-11ee-b77